des: This smart skill is brought to you by the Raghavendra Rathore Jodhpur brand, a lifestyle brand that is known for its Bespoke clothing, personalized accessories, customized products, conceptualization, design & décor for events & weddings, uniform designs and has recently launched a collection of NFT’s. With more than 800 years of history and heritage, the brand is spearheaded by its founder Raghavendra Rathore who belongs to the royal family of Jodhpur and established his label in 1994. Known for its signature Jodhpur Bandhgala, the brand is now synonymous with this classic outfit, not only in India but all over the world.
